  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheese Co-op Clicker Simulator is a multiplayer game where up to 100 players collaborate to amass a mountains of cheese.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/6c93851aadf51b9be815dcd43c9ef966.avif?t=1728253113\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click to get Cheese <br>Click to spend Cheese <br>Click to slay Monsters </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equip The Right Mouse for The Right Task</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/6596ce1381e908f882b5d1a74834d5c0.avif?t=1728253113\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br>By clicking, you get cheese, and you can spend this cheese on a variety of upgrades to boost your Cheese production even further. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheese Co-op Clicker offers a unique and fun gameplay experience with its cooperative mechanics and a multitude of upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/09030b2256d9e0a3091665eb12e6d994.avif?t=1728253113\" width=512 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/7b33298d760992018cdbbec721c2586b.avif?t=1728253113\" width=218 height=306 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/d11d4c04549b1b9fd8d346a1f1f191aa.avif?t=1728253113\" width=512 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UPGRADE Mouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIGHT Monstrers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WORK together with up to 100 players</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheese Co-op Clicker Simulator is a multiplayer game where up to 100 players collaborate to amass a mountains of cheese.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/6c93851aadf51b9be815dcd43c9ef966.avif?t=1728253113\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click to get Cheese <br>Click to spend Cheese <br>Click to slay Monsters </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equip The Right Mouse for The Right Task</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/6596ce1381e908f882b5d1a74834d5c0.avif?t=1728253113\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br>By clicking, you get cheese, and you can spend this cheese on a variety of upgrades to boost your Cheese production even further. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheese Co-op Clicker offers a unique and fun gameplay experience with its cooperative mechanics and a multitude of upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/09030b2256d9e0a3091665eb12e6d994.avif?t=1728253113\" width=512 height=210 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/7b33298d760992018cdbbec721c2586b.avif?t=1728253113\" width=218 height=306 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133580/extras/d11d4c04549b1b9fd8d346a1f1f191aa.avif?t=1728253113\" width=512 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UPGRADE Mouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIGHT Mon